uk.org.lidalia.slf4jtest

Class LoggingEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.org.lidalia.lang.RichObject
      • uk.org.lidalia.slf4jtest.LoggingEvent

  • public class LoggingEvent
extends uk.org.lidalia.lang.RichObject
    Representation of a call to a logger for test assertion purposes.

    The contract of RichObject.equals(Object) and RichObject.hashCode() is that they compare the results of:

    • getLevel()
    • getMdc()
    • getMarker()
    • getThrowable()
    • getMessage()
    • getArguments()

    They do NOT compare the results of getTimestamp() or getCreatingLogger() as this would render it impractical to create appropriate expected LoggingEvents to compare against.

    Constructors and convenient static factory methods exist to create LoggingEvents with appropriate defaults. These are not documented further as they should be self-evident.
